The paper deals with image registration, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a deep learning approach to this problem, which suggests that it may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of probabilistic dense displacement optimization and mean field inference also suggests that it may fall under information theory (cs.IT) or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
